    <h2 class="section-title">Built so the agent can't leak your secret.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">The skill carries critical safety rules the agent must follow before writing a single credential to disk. It's spelled out in plain language at the top of the file.</p>

    <div class="safety">
      <div class="safety-art" aria-hidden="true">
        <div class="lock"><pre><span class="com"># .gitignore</span>
.env                  <span class="ok">✓ added</span>

<span class="com"># source code</span>
<span class="bad">ALLSCALE_SECRET = "st_…"</span>
<span class="com"># refused — secrets never in source</span>

<span class="com"># .env  (gitignored)</span>
ALLSCALE_API_KEY=st_…
ALLSCALE_API_SECRET=st_…</pre></div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-size:22px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.02em;color:var(--text);margin:0 0 6px">Seven non-negotiables.</h3>
